  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0d82\u0da2\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0ddd 50\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c 02\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "02 killed with 50 kilos of ganja",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Navy says that two suspects were arrested yesterday (29th) along with 51 kilos of 500 grams of Kerala Ganja worth more than one million rupees in the Thondamanaru area of \u200b\u200bJaffna.",
        "While inspecting a suspicious van near Thondamanaru Bridge, a group of officers belonging to the Northern Naval Command found this well-hidden Kerala ganja stock in the van and took steps to arrest the driver of the van and another person along with the van.",
        "This stock of Kerala ganja was brought from India by sea and was taken to other parts of the island and thus arrested.",
        "The arrested suspects, aged 39 and 44, are residents of Thondamanaru and the Navy added that they have taken steps to hand over the suspects and the stock of Kerala ganja to the Chhalweli Police for further investigation."
      ],
